    "row": 57,
    "rowsha": "5MeNELbgpX6Dl4Xfj4JxrgrJ9RAYQoFN/87NI3WRj/8=",
    "originContent": ">Regular of noavx2 release?  ",
    "translatedContent": ">Rilis reguler atau noavx2?  "
  },
  {
    "row": 58,
    "rowsha": "smtocOwBjLfMtwJzypn9WBUl619V59kd7BPJMOYFj+I=",
    "originContent": ">Check with Steam if your CPU support avx2. Open Steam, in left corner hover over help menu select System Information and search for AVX2.  ",
    "translatedContent": ">Periksa dengan Steam apakah CPU Anda mendukung avx2. Buka Steam, di pojok kiri arahkan ke menu bantuan lalu pilih Informasi Sistem dan cari AVX2.  "
  },
  {
    "row": 59,
    "rowsha": "zb/B/OHlKrfEqVkWygUjXGiFgd+pn6RgqXUh/jwMFyQ=",
    "originContent": ">If it is supported go with regular release  ",
    "translatedContent": ">Jika didukung gunakan rilis reguler  "
  },
  {
    "row": 60,
    "rowsha": "pKBHSP5zD1tpBVe3afVdTMVHYgNhtDpa/L85E7UMGgk=",
    "originContent": ">If it is not, go with noavx2 release  ",
    "translatedContent": ">Jika tidak, gunakan rilis noavx2  "
  },
  {
    "row": 61,
    "rowsha": "VcRLeaoeZLP2jNj2qTSBTq/hf2NipE0uvmuhROj9+jk=",
    "originContent": "### Fresh Install",
    "translatedContent": "### Instalasi Baru"
  },
  {
    "row": 62,
    "rowsha": "FYbmzIzgKdQ/+LejqSqLMmplx4XgPVQDtGpyCq8sz4A=",
    "originContent": "Download any [supported game](https://github.com/Perchik71/Creation-Kit-Platform-Extended/wiki#brief) and install Creation Kit.  ",
    "translatedContent": "Unduh [game yang didukung](https://github.com/Perchik71/Creation-Kit-Platform-Extended/wiki#brief) lalu instal Creation Kit.  "
  },
  {
